~ set_node_sundial
Narrator: {{State.local_sundial.get_island_name()}} has become the current node island!
do State.node_sundial = State.local_sundial
=> END

~ teleport
if State.has_node_sundial():
	Narrator: Teleport to the current node island, {{State.node_sundial.get_island_name()}}?
	- Yes
		do State.teleport_to_node_sundial.emit()
	- No
		=> END
else:
	Narrator: You don't have a node island right now! Approach a registered island sundial and press G to register a node island.
=> END